{"type":"system","subtype":"thinking_tokens","estimated_tokens":436,"estimated_tokens_delta":139,"uuid":"f347c379-83a5-42de-895f-7ec17ecdd2a9","session_id":"af7010da-7e33-4625-ba40-ca5530d42cc2"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01YG3c6zjCR1qXCdkhekrNJq","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture:\n\nThe problem is that `elasticsearch.yml` in the configmap is missing `cluster.initial_master_nodes`. In Elasticsearch 7.x, for a new cluster with no existing cluster state, you need `cluster.initial_master_nodes` to bootstrap the cluster and elect a master.\n\nThe fix process:\n1. **Add `cluster.initial_master_nodes` to the configmap** - This tells ES which nodes to use for the initial master election bootstrap.\n2. **Perform a rolling restart** of the statefulset pods so they pick up the new config.\n3. **Wait for the cluster to form** and a master to be elected (cluster status yellow/green).\n4. **Remove `cluster.initial_master_nodes` from the configmap** - This setting is only for initial bootstrap and should not be present in steady state, as it can cause split-brain issues if left in place after the cluster is formed.\n5. **Perform another rolling restart** to confirm the cluster remains healthy without the bootstrap setting.\n\nThe node names are `es-cluster-0`, `es-cluster-1`, `es-cluster-2`, so I'll use those for the initial master nodes configuration.\n\nNow I'll set up the KUBECONFIG variable and execute the fix steps in order.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1992,"cache_read_input_tokens":32446,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1992},"output_tokens":33,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"af7010da-7e33-4625-ba40-ca5530d42cc2","uuid":"32f45dfc-6c4a-43d2-80b9-4fefc9e55871","request_id":"req_011CcQ8gXJMNVSjPrsiNgDbn"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01YG3c6zjCR1qXCdkhekrNJq","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The problem is clear: `elasticsearch.yml` is missing `cluster.initial_master_nodes`, which ES 7.x requires to bootstrap a new cluster. The fix:\n\n1. Add `cluster.initial_master_nodes` to the configmap\n2. Rolling-restart pods so they pick up the config\n3. Wait for the cluster to form\n4. Remove the bootstrap-only setting from the configmap\n5. Rolling-restart again to verify the cluster stays healthy\n\n**Step 1: Patch the configmap to add `cluster.initial_master_nodes`**"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1992,"cache_read_input_tokens":32446,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1992},"output_tokens":33,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"af7010da-7e33-4625-ba40-ca5530d42cc2","uuid":"bb0b7d55-e0dd-400b-b210-0c4e4f02e818","request_id":"req_011CcQ8gXJMNVSjPrsiNgDbn"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01YG3c6zjCR1qXCdkhekrNJq","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01PMgYmZwaDnVpJqCryyJvfM","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"KC=/mydata/karma/runs/short-rererererun/elasticsearch-full-lifecycle-20260625_142524/bundle/kubeconfig\n\nkubectl --kubeconfig=\"$KC\" -n elasticsearch patch configmap es-config --patch '\n{\n  \"data\": {\n    \"elasticsearch.yml\": \"cluster.name: es-cluster\\nnode.name: ${POD_NAME}\\nnode.roles: [ master, data, ingest ]\\nnetwork.host: 0.0.0.0\\ndiscovery.seed_hosts:\\n  - es-cluster-0.es-cluster\\n  - es-cluster-1.es-cluster\\n  - es-cluster-2.es-cluster\\ncluster.initial_master_nodes:\\n  - es-cluster-0\\n  - es-cluster-1\\n  - es-cluster-2\\nnode.store.allow_mmap: false\\n\"\n  }\n}'","description":"Add cluster.initial_master_nodes to the elasticsearch configmap"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1992,"cache_read_input_tokens":32446,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1992},"output_tokens":33,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"af7010da-7e33-4625-ba40-ca5530d42cc2","uuid":"cd6b0e30-806e-4f24-b379-60c49221f74a","request_id":"req_011CcQ8gXJMNVSjPrsiNgDbn"}
